# SECURITY & SECRETS

- Never commit secrets; use env vars; provide `.env.example`.
- Add/maintain `.gitignore` for `.env`, `.DS_Store`, `node_modules`, `.venv`, etc.
- For any HTTP call, set timeouts + minimal retries; log errors with context but exclude secrets.
- Sanitize user inputs; validate with pydantic/zod where applicable.
